name: Dynamic Active Mining Opportunities ETF
longDescription: The ETF invests in a concentrated portfolio of primarily equity securities issued by companies that engage directly or indirectly in the exploration, development and production of precious metals, base metals, critical minerals, uranium, rare earths and/or ferrous metals.
